			"strength" => "Rational - Architects see nearly any situation as an opportunity to expand their knowledge and hone their rational thinking skills. 

			Informed - Rather than hunches or half-baked assumptions, they base their conclusions on research and analysis. 
			
			Independent - Conformity is more or less synonymous with mediocrity. Creative and self-motivated, Architects strive to do things their own way.
			
