			"name" => "ENTJ",
			"breakdown" => "Extroverted Intuitive Thinking Judger",
			"definition" => "A Commander (ENTJ) is someone with the Extraverted, Intuitive, Thinking, and Judging personality traits. They are decisive people who love momentum and accomplishment. They gather information to construct their creative visions but rarely hesitate for long before acting on them.

